<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Apply joints===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* A Revolute joint between Axle1 and Fork001
</div>

[[Image:Assembly3_UniversalJointExample-02.png|200px]]
